Smart Email Labeling AI Agent

This AI agent reads your incoming emails, figures out what they’re about, and adds clear labels to them in your inbox.

So you can see at a glance if an email is about work, a partnership, a collab, or anything else — without opening it.

Great for:
- Sales reps  
- Business developers  
- YouTubers & KOLs  
- Anyone who gets a lot of emails
